      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/f1717-stiffness-qoi-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "QoI comparison — construct stiffness: FEA vs. bench (N=11, two labs)",
      "description": "FEA ensemble mean construct stiffness differed from experimental mean by 4.2% (lab 1) and 5.8% (lab 2). E/uval = 0.87 and 1.12 respectively, both below the 1.96 threshold. Acceptance criterion satisfied for stiffness QoI."
    },
    {
