      "description": "FEA ensemble mean yield force differed from experimental mean by 7.1% (lab 1) and 6.3% (lab 2). E/uval = 1.41 and 1.28 respectively. Acceptance criterion satisfied for yield force QoI."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/f1717-force-40mm-qoi-comparison",
