      "name": "QoI comparison — force at 40 mm displacement: FEA vs. bench (N=11, two labs)",
      "description": "FEA ensemble mean force at 40 mm displacement differed from experimental mean by 8.9% (lab 1) and 7.4% (lab 2). E/uval = 1.61 and 1.44 respectively. Acceptance criterion satisfied for force-at-displacement QoI."
    }
  ],
